<h1>Darfur: The evidence of war crimes</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline"><!--proximic_content_on-->500 drawings by children who escaped the violence are to be submitted to the International Criminal Court as proof of war crimes by Sudanese forces<!--proximic_content_off--></p>
	<div class="photoCaption" style="width: 294px; margin-left: 10px;">
       <a href="javascript:launchPopup('https://web.archive.org/web/20080422162206/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/darfur-the-evidence-of-war-crimes-459922.html?action=Popup&amp;gallery=no','', 670, 1061, true, true, true, false);">
